org.mapstruct.ap.internal.util.workarounds

Class TypesDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mapstruct.ap.internal.util.workarounds.TypesDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Types

    public class TypesDecorator
extends Object
implements Types
    Replaces the usage of Types within MapStruct by delegating to the original implementation or to our specific workarounds if necessary.
    Author:
    Andreas Gudian
